snippet.title: Justyna Steczkowska - GAJA (Eurovision 2025 Poland)
snippet.description:
Winner of the Grand Final of the Polish National Selection for Eurovision 2025 and a representative at the Eurovision contest in 2025.

The Eurovision song "GAJA" by Justyna Steczkowska is a manifestation of personal power and transcendence. Gaja – Mother Earth – becomes a symbol of divinity, strength, and love. The artist combines both the divine and human spheres in her character. The cry of Gaja has the power to transform the world. As a mother and guardian figure, she has control over time and destiny. She also holds the power to transform the world, becoming a symbol of regaining control over one's own destiny and time.

Listen to the new album, WITCH TAROHORO, out now: https://e-muzyka.link/JustynaSteczkowskaWITCHTAROHORO

snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto VI Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Vice City, USA.

Jason and Lucia have always known the deck is stacked against them. But when an easy score goes wrong, they find themselves on the darkest side of the sunniest place in America, in the middle of a criminal conspiracy stretching across the state of Leonida — forced to rely on each other more than ever if they want to make it out alive. 

Explore Vice City and beyond at https://www.rockstargames.com/VI

This trailer was captured entirely in-game from a PlayStation 5, comprised of equal parts gameplay and cutscenes.
